%!PS-Adobe-3.0 EPSF-3.0
%%BoundingBox: 0 0 400 300
%%Title: Simple Shapes
%%EndComments

% Background
0.94 0.94 0.94 setrgbcolor
0 0 400 300 rectfill

% Red rectangle
0.91 0.30 0.24 setrgbcolor
20 200 100 80 rectfill

% Blue circle
0.20 0.60 0.86 setrgbcolor
230 240 50 0 360 arc fill

% Green ellipse
0.18 0.80 0.44 setrgbcolor
gsave 350 100 translate 40 60 scale 0 0 1 0 360 arc fill grestore

%%EOF
